# Snyk Python Scan - Local Instructions

1. Install Snyk CLI:
   brew install snyk/tap/snyk

2. Authenticate:
   snyk auth

3. Navigate to project directory:
   cd <<path>>

4. Run a scan:
   snyk test --file=requirements.txt --package-manager=pip --fail-on=upgradable

5. (Optional) Monitor project:
   snyk monitor --file=requirements.txt --package-manager=pip
